Global Parecoxib Sodium Injection Market Insights
Parecoxib Sodium Injection Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Parecoxib Sodium Injection Market Overview
The global Parecoxib Sodium Injection market size was valued at approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to register a CAGR of 6.4% from 2025 to 2032. This steady growth is driven by the increasing use of Parecoxib Sodium for pain management and its ability to provide efficient analgesic effects in various surgical procedures. The rising prevalence of chronic diseases, such as osteoarthritis and cancer, coupled with a growing geriatric population, is significantly contributing to the market’s growth. Additionally, the increase in elective surgeries globally is expected to create a demand for post-operative pain management, further boosting the market for Parecoxib Sodium Injection in the forecast period.

